site_name:
Hadley House 
Hadley Green Road
Barnet
EN5 5PR
description: Non material amendments to planning permission B/03009/11 dated 31/08/2011 for ` Demolition of rear extension and pergola structure, addition of new rear extension and orangery to walled garden, refurbishment and alterations to layouts, including installation of an indoor pool.' Amendments include installation of two reproduction 18th Century fireplaces to second floor bathroom and hallway. Retention of internal alterations comprising reorientation of stairway and glass balastrading to plant room stair; new wc to entrance hall; creation of wardrobe area and installation of staircase to loft; within Pool Room repositioning of new stair, relocation of changing facilities,introduction of access door, alterations to mezzanine gallery and installation of maintenance access door; alteration to external openings including replacing proposed door  and the reinstatement four windows  to stable block; introduction of access stairway to clock mechanism and further bathroom to stable block west wing; alterations to  Annex building including alterations to internal layout, relocation of entrance door to west elevation, introduction of two additional windows to front elevation , in place of a door, relocation of vehicle gate to garden side; Outbuilding and hardsurfacing lowered by 200mm, reclaimed  granite setts used  for hardsurfacing, extension of and an additional 200mm added to outbuilding parapet wall,  alteration to design of outbuildings to include open car port and amendment of window and door position.
